data.description: Fantastic Jamestown location!! Just blocks from amazing restaurants, shopping, music venues and parks and High Point Lake! This great traditional Forestdale home features a picket fenced lush lot, with 4 bedrooms upstairs and a private spa room.  The main level includes a well appointed kitchen and a bright recreation room that overlooks the backyard. The main level garage boasts a workshop and ample storage. The oversized courtyard features a built in fireplace and pergola perfect for entraining or your own personal retreat! Newer water filtration system. Pool table and porch swing can convey. Schedule your showing today!
